com.psddev.dari.util

Interface PullThroughReference<K,V>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PullThroughReference.Soft, PullThroughReference.Strong, PullThroughReference.Weak

    public interface PullThroughReference<K,V>
    Reference to a value created in the pull-through classes.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  PullThroughReference.Soft<K,V>
      PullThroughReference implementation that may lose its value under memory pressure.
      static class  PullThroughReference.Strong<K,V>
      PullThroughReference implementation that holds onto its value forever.
      static class  PullThroughReference.Weak<K,V>
      PullThroughReference implementation that may lose its value when there are no other references.
